{"tid":2274980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登——咱们的新总统","createTime":"2020-11-06T22:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T00:34:43.000Z","uid":334191,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7384312610baa92af9bdb5e8a50c13f23e270d66","tid":2274980,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:10:25.000Z","msg":"宾州点票即将结束，一万多票逆袭，仅此选举人票就可突破273。<br />\n拜登最终的选举人票将在300张以上，但这有赖于关键州的微小优势。<br />\n赢了，赢得艰难而侥幸，战术上不是大胜，战略上是溃败。<br />\n按照连登的标准，有一半美国人不是港人臆想的左胶就是港人设定的共特。<br />\n按照林肯的标准，有一半美国人支持或默许种族主义、仇恨、专制和败坏。<br />\n祝福千疮百孔的旧美国，祝贺步履蹒跚的新总统。<br />\n她不是山巅之城，从来不是；他不是中流砥柱，不可能是。<br />\n希望很遥远，未来依旧在。<br />\n光复美国，时代革命。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJunHYW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJunHYW.jpg&h=f529421b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90ab4a9bffdcaee38b6698fc7e61c38084c4011d","tid":2274980,"uid":367153,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0wUy6J.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0wUy6J.gif&h=7b478f27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8af8695a9adb8ed85417695ec3056fb5b10c5184","tid":2274980,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:15:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dff4f860efa507c291bc9f4d0be740b5e6c4851d","tid":2274980,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:20:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/slmngy001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fslmngy001&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=4ed1cc98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/slmngy001</a>"},{"pid":"e394248ef588027f9b6e44fcfeec8c6eaee9f60b","tid":2274980,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T22:24:58.000Z","msg":"拜特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"